fields.description:
NOT a regression, occurs in 3.1.3.GA as well.
h5. To reproduce
1) Package KS for mobile web and open on iOS devices Safari browser
2) Navigate to Base UI>Views>Image Views> Table Views> Delete Row
3) Click Delete Row till last row is gone
h5. Actual result
{code}
[INFO] deleting row 0
{code}
h5. Expected result
{code}
[WARN] No row found for index: 0
{code}
